Feature: Activate roadstead

	As user
	I want to be able to activate the GPS or radar.
	So that know if in the area where I am located at  that moment someone can be located who could 	endanger my life.

Acceptance criteria:
	*The user must confirm password to make 	changes
	*Company members require authorization from theiremployer to make changes
	
	Scenario: Activate roadstead
	 Given that the user is in the Radar option within the application.
	 When you click on the “Activate Radar“ button
   Then the system request to activate the GPS of your 	 device and you will be able to see in real time if any danger is located by area.
